{"id": "art-1441", "label": "Art. 1441", "title": "Art. 1441", "slug": "art-1441", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_477351992\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2187\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_477351992\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 144<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_799238823\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2186\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_799238823\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Membrii consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\n<span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> vor exercita mandatul cu <span class=SpellE>pruden&#355;a</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> diligenta unui bun administrator.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_750174708\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2185\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_750174708\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Administratorul nu încalc&#259; <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ia</span>\nprev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (1), dac&#259; în momentul lu&#259;rii unei\ndecizii de afaceri el este în mod rezonabil <span class=SpellE>îndrept&#259;&#355;it</span>\ns&#259; considere c&#259; <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ioneaz&#259;</span> în\ninteresul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\npe baza unor <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> adecvate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_497434665\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2184\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_497434665\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Decizie de afaceri, în sensul prezentei <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legi</i>, este orice decizie de a lua sau de\na nu lua anumite m&#259;suri cu privire la administrarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1800375716\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2183\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1800375716\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Membrii consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\n<span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> vor exercita mandatul cu loialitate, în\ninteresul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_754991469\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2182\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_754991469\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Membrii consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\nnu vor divulga <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;iile</span> <span class=SpellE>confiden&#355;iale</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> secretele comerciale ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\nla care au acces în calitatea lor de administratori. Aceast&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;ie</span> le revine <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ndup&#259; încetarea mandatului de administrator.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_844446114\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2181\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_844446114\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)<span class=SpellE>Con&#355;inutul</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> durata <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (5) sunt stipulate în contractul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}